Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:12.41,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You went and brought more junk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:22.21,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You're so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:27.42,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Sorry I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.33,0:00:33.06,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:37.35,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I want you to stay by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:44.12,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Please. Let's stay by each other forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.99,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,That's exactly why I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:54.82,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,...so that we can be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:33.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, do you have everything you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:34.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've got 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:38.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shio-chan. Say "goodbye".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:44.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.10,San,San,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:54.03,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 16
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:54.03,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}White Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san is with Nagisa during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The old man comes frequently, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:07.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everyone's doing the best they can so Nagisa can deliver Ushio safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.30,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:22.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,At times, I'm scared that you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:29.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If Nagisa hadn't met me, she wouldn't have to go through this life or death delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I changed Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:38.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When I first met her, she looked really weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:42.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,{\fs78.3}So weak it made me think she would've stayed standing at the foot of the hill if I hadn't spoken to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was giving myself too much credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I thought she became stronger because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And I thought I became stronger because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.06,San,San,0,0,0,,That's exactly right, Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:04:00.82,San,San,0,0,0,,Both Akio-san and I are very grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I'm starting to question things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If I weren't here, she would still be at your home,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,and though she might have had less friends, she would be living a happy life of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:16.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If not, she might have met someone better than me and be having a happier life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.57,San,San,0,0,0,,We can't imagine such a thing, Tomoya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:24.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I knew you'd say that since you're a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.41,San,San,0,0,0,,I mean it from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:32.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry; I acted like a child there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.76,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I continued to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.75,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,A machine that flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:48.58,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I will make the machine that will take us from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.90,Note,,0,0,0,,Sign: Tonari-machi Hospital - lit. "Neighboring City Hospital"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.07,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's almost Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And your birthday at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What do you want this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.54,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The Big Dango Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's the point of collecting more of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Besides, you won't find them anywhere anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:23.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Would it be hard to find?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's probably impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.56,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,How did you find that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:41.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun went through lots of trouble to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:44.57,San,San,0,0,0,,How does getting one every year sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.32,San,San,0,0,0,,You'll eventually get a real "big family".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:50.37,San,San,0,0,0,,The older ones will probably get jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:55.01,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But I can't hug all three at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:57.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So I want you to hug them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:01.17,San,San,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:05.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, you look adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can smell Nagisa on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yo. Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey! We went through this last April!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:34.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san. Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:37.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagisa-chan. Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.00,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Whoa!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.18,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It gets this big, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This is almost mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.61,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.12,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Stop being so tactless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:57.83,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You haven't changed even though\Nyou've become a member of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.77,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, I don't think you can talk about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kyou. Fujibayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:06.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.57,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.07,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I came back from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:14.33,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Happy New Year to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.01,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.51,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,May I touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:25.96,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.59,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's very wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.69,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Me! I'm up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.43,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.85,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.27,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,The rice cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:44.02,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So this is Tomoyo's family, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Her brother looks well, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We have one from Miyazawa-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Looks like everyone is getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:54.62,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This one is from Nishina-san and Sugisaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:58.35,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,They're saying to do your best to have a healthy baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Give this to Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.14,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san's latest release.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He started singing again as an indie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:13.68,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,"Lobe and Spannier"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.51,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You read that "Love and Spanner".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.97,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Did you really graduate from high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.08,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,It's a very distinctive title.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san and I came up with the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:27.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We got it to sound as normal as we could. {I wish they made the title selection process to anime. It was hilarious.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.40,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.61,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, they're both Okazaki now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.53,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then, Okazaki-guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What kinda name is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:44.25,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What does it feel like to become a father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What a strange thing to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.90,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'm interested in hearing your thoughts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:52.13,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,What does it feel like to become a parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:57.51,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I thought becoming a parent is something way in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:03.51,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But hearing you two were going to be parents, it suddenly felt much more "real".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:08.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I probably shouldn't say this in front of you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,but no one becomes a father because they want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.64,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I consider it more like a natural hazard like an earthquake or lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:20.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So I want to know what's in\Nyour mind as you become a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:24.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.72,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:32.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm not sure if it registers that I'm going to be a father yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:37.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But, I found a person I can love,\Nand this happened when I lived for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:42.10,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,In the end, Okazaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,you haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:52.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It felt like you and Nagisa-chan became distant, but you weren't so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Glad I found that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:59.29,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was actually nervous until I saw you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.83,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It felt like you two were way ahead in the life game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.15,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Life is very mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.95,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Where does it come from, and where does it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:14.59,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm researching the same thing my father and mother were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.29,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The hidden world, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.35,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:28.22,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's another world that exists right next to this one, but it can't be seen or felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:33.45,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But we're starting to find out that's not entirely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.14,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:35.88,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:39.37,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's probably akin to a warped extra dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:46.18,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,The current theory states that what we perceive as objects are stuck firm to high dimension planes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:49.90,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,...and they cannot remove themselves from their maximum existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:55.59,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But, for example, energy due to gravity is said to transcend through dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.19,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Just like that-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:58.29,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.97,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tell us the story so we can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:04.58,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,That was a very, very simplified explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:10.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,{\fs78.3}So you're saying that this world and the hidden world\Nare related strongly at a deep level?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.17,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:20.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,{\fs78.3}Time, space, and people's minds echo in a strange way to recreate both worlds or create whole new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:23.18,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,They might be affecting each other like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.66,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:29.08,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Could our lives be tied to that world, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:33.09,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Maybe, then yet again maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:36.59,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This world is really filled with mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:40.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I wonder what the hidden world is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:49.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What? Why did I just think of that play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The girl in the world that ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:55.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why did I know that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:03.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In that other world, people might be having parties like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:07.92,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,There may be more than one hidden world. {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:11.46,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,There's a theory of multiple worlds existing, too. {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:13.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Fujibayashi. {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:17.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I remember you saying something like that when you were talking about fortune-telling. {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:22.58,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Yes. There is no one future,\Nbut there are many possibilities. {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:24.35,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I still think that. {ep 15}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:32.69,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then there could be a world where one of you is dating me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.40,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Not a chance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.96,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'd reject you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:48.80,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I can't create anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:52.35,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,All I can do is pile up the junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.68,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,No matter how much effort I put in, it was useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.46,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I had stopped working at a certain point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So you were here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.02,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The city will continue to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:20.09,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nothing can stay as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:24.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's what it means to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:28.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But isn't this an important place for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:33.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If I interfered with this construction, would Nagisa be able to stay well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's an idea that's crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:43.05,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous. It's a great thing for the people of this city for this hospital to be built.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.08,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,It's not something we can mess with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:49.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm coming to hate this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:56.40,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I asked people involved with the construction to preserve some trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.02,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Tomo-pyon did something similar, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Tomo-pyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Tomoyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:05.35,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I heard you guys decided to deliver at a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:08.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's more reassuring to be in a place where there's equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.95,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Walk over, wait, and pray, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.34,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We might get some snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That night, we were buried with snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:29.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,With neither trains nor cars able to move, the city froze as if it had gotten sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:35.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Nagisa caught a fever,\Nand the contractions started at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:39.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was labor two weeks earlier than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa! Hang in there, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:04.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I will give birth to Shio-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:09.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I will live with you and Shio-chan. The three of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.24,San,San,0,0,0,,Yagi-san's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.93,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,The cars can't move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.21,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Why did this come on a day like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:19.84,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san. Please prepare hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:20.94,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,As much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:21.98,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:26.01,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san. You keep supporting your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's all right to hold on to her hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.83,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Of course. Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa. I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't lose, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You will give birth fine and start a new life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,With Ushio, a new life for the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.29,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Don't worry, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.30,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,There now, breathe out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.70,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.10,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.35,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Yes, loosen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.00,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Yes, good. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.28,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Shall I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa passed out multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And she woke up to the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:26.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was so cruel that I wanted to look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:38.79,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was long, and it felt like it was going to continue without end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even I felt as though I was going to pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:48.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Perhaps, my mind couldn't take any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Or perhaps, I despaired over everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:17.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:20.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:23.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya...kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:37.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm here! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You can hear it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The voice of our child crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.65,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:51.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Look. I'm the first one to hug her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:07.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a girl! A lively girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:11.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was able to have her at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:17.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Though, I made Shio-chan go through extra trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:20.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well done... You've done a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:26.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, I'm a little tired now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:31.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,May I rest for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.78,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:35.29,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Damn it! Is the doctor still not here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.25,Default,Yag,0,0,0,,Cars still can't move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:40.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa... Hold on, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:44.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,L-Let's talk for a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You can just listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Look, it's our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She looks like a monkey, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So small, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm going to call to her now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:04.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm your daddy, Ushio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's your mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:06.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:12.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course. She doesn't understand what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:22.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll grow fast, enter elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:28.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then we'd go to the open house and sports day together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:30.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll participate as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:34.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I used to be the one that scoffed at stuff like that the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:41.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:51.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Feel that? It's Ushio's cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah? Feel that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:04.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You said you'll always be with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:11.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You said you'll always be with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:18.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We... We promised we will, many times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:26.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"There's nothing good even if I lived."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:29.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,"It's a boring life."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:33.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a dream a guy, who used to think things like that, finally found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey... Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:38.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:41.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:02.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you like this school? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I really, really love it. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:12.14,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But nothing can stay unchanged. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:14.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Fun things... Happy things...{S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:17.63,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They can't all possibly stay unchanged. {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:21.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Even so, can you keep on loving this place? {S1 ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:34.01,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If only we'd never met...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:37.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We should have taken different paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:43.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have dated Nagisa, nor would I have married her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:46.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ushio wouldn't have been born, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:50.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then this sadness would never have haunted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:03.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I should never have met her.
